      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_380508" metaid="metaid_57" name="Translocation of NuMA to the centrosomes" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">After the nuclear envelope breakdown, phosphorylated NuMA rapidly moves to the centrosomal region (Compton and Luo 1995, Hsu and Yeh 1996, Kotak et al. 2013).</p>
        </notes>
