      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2529015" metaid="metaid_59" name="Dephosphorylation of CK2-modified condensin I" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Inhibitory phosphate groups that were added to condensin I subunits by CK2 during interphase have to be removed for full mitotic activation of condensin I (Takemoto et al. 2006). The responsible phosphatase has not been identified.</p>
        </notes>
