      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2545253" metaid="metaid_67" name="Deacetylation of cohesin" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">HDAC8 deacetylates cohesin in prometaphase, after cohesin dissociates from chromosomal arms (Deardorff et al. 2012).</p>
