      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_9851972" metaid="metaid_78" name="PLK1 phosphorylates FIRRM at S43" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">PLK1 phosphorylates FIRRM (also known as Apolo1 or FLIP) at serine residue S43, which increases the binding affinity of FIRRM for PLK1 (Xu et al. 2021).</p>
        </notes>
